  "StockRole": "Brawler",
  "YangsThoughts": "The Reaver is a one-of-a-kind machine, built by Firefly Foundry from the ground up for Firefly Stables to compete in Solaris VII assault-class tournaments starting in 3073. Arena mechs get designed around a very different set of priorities than battlefield machines, and this one shows it, with a Fluid Gun for limiting the opponents strength and a Lance for crowd-pleasing melee work alongside the conventional weapons. Getting something purpose-built for the Games into field service is always an interesting problem to solve.",
